entries.title: Janet Programming Language
entries.description: Janet is a functional and imperative programming language. It runs on Windows, Linux, macOS, and should run on other systems with some porting. The entire language (core library, interpreter, compiler, assembler) is less than 1MB while offering a very rich language and should run on many constrained systems.
